  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc0\u0ba9 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bc1\u0bb5 \u0b95\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb2\u0bcd : \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe : \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Chinese military observation ship arriving at Ambandottai: India is very dissatisfied: Sri Lanka is requested to clarify",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Delhi has expressed strong displeasure over the visit of the Chinese military surveillance ship Yuan Wong-5 to Sri Lanka and has requested the government to provide a complete clarification on the reason for the ship's visit and its activities during the time it was anchored at Ambantota port.",
        "A high-level message from Delhi has been conveyed to Colombo that the arrival of the Chinese military observation and inspection ship has a direct impact on India's national security issues.",
        "The Yuan Wong-5 military observation vessel will visit the port of Ambantota on the 11th of August at 11 p.m. Yuan Wong-5 has started its journey to Sri Lanka from the port of Jiangxi through the East China Sea. Yuan Wong-5 is capable of carrying out ship surveillance operations using satellite and state-of-the-art satellite technology.",
        "Yuan Wang-5 is China's most modern surveillance ship. On the other hand, it has various modern surveillance facilities, including the ability to monitor the launch of missiles and intercontinental ballistic missiles. The US said the ship was operated by the Chinese military's strategic brigade.",
        "Several countries had warned Sri Lanka that China might use the Ambantota port as its military base.",
        "In such a situation, India has expressed strong dissatisfaction and opposition. As far as the Sri Lanka-Indian waters are concerned, both sides are dealing on the basis of mutual benefits. Therefore, it is noteworthy that Delhi has told Sri Lanka that it cannot accept the kind of movements that threaten India's national security."
      ],
